        "hashtags": "#AI #GPT5 #Automation #AIThatScales",
        "platforms": "Facebook + Instagram",
        "post_text": "The game just changed — again.\n\nOpenAI dropped GPT-5 this morning and the reasoning capability leap is real. I've been testing it since 6 AM and the difference isn't subtle.\n\nFor business owners: this isn't theoretical anymore. The automation workflows that felt \"almost there\" last year? They're \"fully there\" now.\n\nWe're already updating 3 client systems this week. If you haven't started automating your operations, you're now 2 generations behind.\n\nDM me if you want to talk about what this means for your business.\n\n#AI #GPT5 #Automation #AIThatScales #BusinessAutomation #FutureOfWork"
