        "post_text": "New data out: AI agents handle 40% of customer service interactions at Fortune 500 companies.\n\nThat's not a pilot program. That's operational reality.\n\nThe companies winning aren't waiting for \"perfect\" AI — they're deploying 80% solutions and improving in real-time.\n\nYour competitors are already doing this. The question is whether you're building the system or getting left behind.\n\nWhat's your biggest customer service bottleneck right now?\n\n#CustomerService #AIAgents #Automation #SmallBusiness #AIThatScales"
