        "post_text": "Case study: AI-powered guest comms cut response time from 4 hours to 8 minutes across a 40-property portfolio.\n\nNot theoretical — I've seen it firsthand with Stay Coastal's 30+ properties.\n\nGuests don't care if a bot answered. They care that someone answered. Fast responses = better reviews = more bookings.\n\nMath is simple. Setup takes a weekend. ROI is permanent.\n\nRunning STRs and still answering every message manually? Let's talk.\n\n#VacationRental #PropertyManagement #AI #Airbnb #ShortTermRental #AIThatScales"
